dc_title_s: Map of a survey showing the location of islands numbered one to twenty-three in Barnegat Bay, Ocean County, New Jersey
dc_description_s: This is a map of the islands in Barnegat Bay near the Barnegat Bay Lighthouse. The islands are numbered one to twenty-three and the location of the Barnegat Bay Lighthouse and life saving stations are noted.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
